<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Linux Usage on kmdr blog</title><link>https://km0e.github.io/zh-cn/categories/linux/</link><description>Recent content in Linux Usage on kmdr blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><atom:link href="https://km0e.github.io/zh-cn/categories/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Soft Router</title><link>https://km0e.github.io/zh-cn/p/soft-router/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 13:50:03 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://km0e.github.io/zh-cn/p/soft-router/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="记配置软路由的过程">记配置软路由的过程
&lt;/h1>&lt;h2 id="1-环境">1. 环境
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>使用修改后的&lt;a class="link" href="https://km0e.github.io/zh-cn/p/utils/#1.1 linux 服务器测试脚本" >&lt;code>bench.sh&lt;/code>&lt;/a>脚本，探测到的环境如下：
&lt;img src="https://km0e.github.io/image.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="alt text"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-linux配置">2. Linux配置
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>换源，来自&lt;a class="link" href="https://help.mirrorz.org/debian/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>MirrorZ&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">18
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">su -c &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;cat &amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;#39;EOF&amp;#39; &amp;gt; /etc/apt/sources.list
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># 默认注释了源码镜像以提高 apt update 速度，如有需要可自行取消注释
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-updates main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-updates main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-backports main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian/ bookworm-backports main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># 以下安全更新软件源包含了官方源与镜像站配置，如有需要可自行修改注释切换
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># deb-src https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># deb https://security.debian.org/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2"># # deb-src https://security.debian.org/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">EOF&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
